      "content": "I hear you on the performance side, but the safety board is pretty firm. They've decided that a slight delay in response is a better trade-off than the risk of an autonomous system making a \"creative\" decision that leads to a crash. They're basically saying that being predictable is more important than being smart. It's just the way it has to be for us to get certified.",
